Interface NavigatorConfigurator

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ListNavigatorConfiguratorImpl, NavigatorConfiguratorBean, NavigatorConfiguratorImpl, RichListNavigatorConfiguratorImpl
public interface NavigatorConfigurator
extends java.io.Serializable

This interface is the input of the TreeView task flow. Its main aim is to ensure the model and uiConfiguration objects are not duplicated inside the TreeView taskflow bean after serialization/deserialization.
